description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 66, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 132, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 1 for East, Stringalong for South, and 1 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50662-41712-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [132 Votes, Top 15% Score]
